Docs.remarks:
This will be triggered NOT ONLY on buttons inside the rows and cols of the datagrid. It will be trigered on pager click or other items...


You must use e.Item.ItemType to determine the type of the DataGrid item selected. 
e.Item will return an object of the type 
if(e.Item.ItemType == ListItemType.Item)
{
	// We have a Item of one row of the dataset
	...
}
else if(e.Item.ItemType == ListItemType.Pager)
{
	// We made click on the pager item of the grid
	...
}
